review: The binder is pretty generic and serves it's purpose.  This is a review of the packaging and delivery only.  The first delivery looked like it had got wet and then sat for a while.  There was rust some of the rivets and moisture in the cover insert area.  The second delivery was fine.
productTitle: Wilson Jones Round Ring View Binder, 1.5 Inch, Basic, 362 Series, Customizable, White, 4 Pack (W70362-34WPP)
